partners across the country that

00:36:14.800 --> 00:36:18.283
work with young people to try
to create these catalytic models

00:36:18.283 --> 00:36:20.200
so that there are more
options for communities

00:36:20.200 --> 00:36:23.810
that they can learn from, be
inspired by, and borrow from.

00:36:23.810 --> 00:36:25.630
The second role that
we play is that we're

00:36:25.630 --> 00:36:27.400
supporting a broader
range of communities

00:36:27.400 --> 00:36:30.197
everywhere to build their demand
and readiness for this work.

00:36:30.197 --> 00:36:31.780
