even more latent demand,

00:36:35.950 --> 00:36:38.710
like what kids actually want,
the dreams that they actually

00:36:38.710 --> 00:36:40.255
have, what parents
want, et cetera.

00:36:40.255 --> 00:36:42.130
We've started to realize
that we can actually

00:36:42.130 --> 00:36:44.725
work with communities to
build a set of conditions that

00:36:44.725 --> 00:36:46.600
accelerate their movement
