but the change can
actually sustain,

00:37:02.950 --> 00:37:05.492
because parents are part of it,
and employers are part of it,

00:37:05.492 --> 00:37:07.412
committee members are
part of it, et cetera.

00:37:07.412 --> 00:37:09.370
So these are essentially
the two kinds of roles

00:37:09.370 --> 00:37:10.453
that we're trying to play.

