00:38:04.527 --> 00:38:05.860
There's a lot that we can learn.

00:38:05.860 --> 00:38:07.660
And so we're building
a hub of knowledge

00:38:07.660 --> 00:38:09.130
that people can draw from.

00:38:09.130 --> 00:38:12.100
And then the third is a network,
