00:38:16.630 --> 00:38:18.205
We've seen that
change moves fastest

00:38:18.205 --> 00:38:19.330
when networks are involved.

00:38:19.330 --> 00:38:20.600
And so we're building
this network, as well.

00:38:20.600 --> 00:38:22.850
Those are the three pieces
of what we're trying to do.

